REQUIREMENTS:
-PCL LIBRARY (sudo apt-get install pcl-tools | sudo apt install libpcl-dev)
-cmake (sudo apt-get install cmake)

cd build
cmake ..
make
./cluster_extraction

------


IMPORTANT:
You have to change the following line of code:
  std::vector<boost::filesystem::path> stream(boost::filesystem::directory_iterator{"/media/nacho/DATA/AD_course_2020_code/Sensors/pcl/dataset_1/"},
                                             boost::filesystem::directory_iterator{});

into the path that contains your dataset 
